Software Engineer

We are looking for a talented Software Engineer to join our development team. This role involves designing, developing, and maintaining software applications.

About the Role
As a Software Engineer, you will work on building scalable web applications, writing clean and maintainable code, and collaborating with cross-functional teams. You will participate in code reviews, contribute to technical documentation, and help improve our development processes.

About Required Skills
- Python
- JavaScript
- Web Development
- RESTful APIs
- Database Design
- Git
- Agile Methodologies
- Problem Solving
- Software Testing
- Code Review

What You Will Do
- Design and implement new features for web applications
- Write unit tests and maintain code quality
- Collaborate with product managers and designers
- Participate in sprint planning and daily standups
- Debug and fix software issues

What We Offer
- Competitive salary and benefits
- Remote work flexibility
- Professional development opportunities
- Collaborative team environment

How to Apply
Please submit your resume and a cover letter describing your relevant experience.
